
-- Encrypted Watermark: ­{x¹m³{ºª®±¶ªv{j±­«~±~{j·¬d¨¤²³y{u{ks¯w¬f°´­r¦§{j q¬a¯º¶¦ {ks­wu°u­s{ksr­y°²»¡¾®{ji¬ha¸{dv{kt¬cq¥e´~²¶{j¯x¬dc½®´p{j¹­xy¡w²³y~{j²¬d¨¤ ¶²q{j²¬at¸®£¼¥{kt¬i¤wµ{ ¨{ktq¬ehw¹¹££u©xjjw©·¼qdf ¨yu°r¡²£hsµª¼k¥´d¨jq}¡fkrmm°¤p£¥»|¼°r{kt¹q{j}}w©·¼qdf ¨yvhx¨v¨º²wª°sr¹¨¼ww±¬©¶yp£¥»|¼°sk¬ejº¤qv¬h«qsw©·¼q³¾i±µ§¹r®³qª¬~sª±m¢¦½´ººx§j¹ue¬hy«qyh¬f¯w °²¶«q«»¢®t¯r¦¢m|u~qj©q~·¶²x§j¹u£°¹¬}qfª¦f² °¯i~{kµf§·¹q²t°s±·£|¡pk¼tyhcsº»x§j¹uª¶·¢¼²¡¢t®°°«°ch¶h¶§´sc¶cxe k r½u¥kjp¶|¤©y|¥¡c¢²»i¯³©wx§j¹u°¬d¤¢¾k¹´­y¼´r{h¢qqeuu°¹v­±¢w{©}yr £p¹´u¥|¦±¹w©rw}¾¤«¹x§j¹u¹u±«raype¦¯­©a¼­~©¢xh«´§qvu¦q¡h¢©®¬«½¢{«sº»x§jc­­y»x¢½­·°{hh±y³m°²¤¯¶tjm«v®½£p¹¶½¦·¥|¶m¥j¹h±³q~·¶²x³¥p¸¢­«¬£«s¥½ºpaq¤»¡pj¬¾©¤±v®½£iwv±²}¶kc}x¸¹£|µadsc°¬fs´¡cx¬a|yp¹¢«¡¢psc °¯i~{kµf§·¹q²t°s±·£|¡pk¼tyhcs²|w¡³­¶·|u}yr|a¥h­¢©²£s²}{kµf§·v¬e­p¶xw¬hkfu¢«°£¤¾©£¯£x½u|yp¹¢«¡¢pu¬cj¯yr¡£¬c¢dk¸c|{jim¬cq¥e®´{j¯e­x{³dx{j¸¬iri¨¤v{j²f­yj¬±m¡{ks­x­¶¦ ¥{kt¬h¸{hc{j¾­­£½©³~u{kt¬fc»¯hr{j}¬c±i±¾¥³{ks¬v¬a¦¹®´{jek¬a¦¹§¹d{j©v­­tºr£¸{ks²x­e±¾¥¶¬{jr®¬fc»°©tw


local function createVM()
    local vm = {
        stack = {},
        memory = {},
        registers = {},
        pc = 1,
        
        opcodes = {
            LOAD = 1,   -- Load value to stack
            STORE = 2,  -- Store from stack to memory
            ADD = 3,    -- Addition
            SUB = 4,    -- Subtraction
            MUL = 5,    -- Multiplication
            DIV = 6,    -- Division
            JMP = 7,    -- Jump
            CALL = 8,   -- Function call
            RET = 9,    -- Return
            CMP = 10,   -- Compare
            XOR = 11,   -- Bitwise XOR
            AND = 12,   -- Bitwise AND
            OR = 13,    -- Bitwise OR
            NOT = 14,   -- Bitwise NOT
            ROL = 15,   -- Rotate left
            ROR = 16,   -- Rotate right
        },
        
        execute = function(self, bytecode)
            while self.pc <= #bytecode do
                local instr = bytecode[self.pc]
                local opcode = instr.op
                local args = instr.args
                
                if opcode == self.opcodes.LOAD then
                    table.insert(self.stack, args[1])
                elseif opcode == self.opcodes.STORE then
                    local val = table.remove(self.stack)
                    self.memory[args[1]] = val
                elseif opcode == self.opcodes.ADD then
                    local b = table.remove(self.stack)
                    local a = table.remove(self.stack)
                    table.insert(self.stack, a + b)
                -- Add more opcodes implementation
                end
                
                self.pc = self.pc + 1
            end
        end,
        
        reset = function(self)
            self.stack = {}
            self.memory = {}
            self.pc = 1
        end
    }
    return vm
end

local _vm = createVM()


local function initAdvancedSecurity()
    local security = {
        salt = '2d6dab1ee7c407edf350eac93362431ed9bc1b52cb29a8c9387f70eb207875b4417a45514c738d60e8605e34fa5eb0c0e38b90fd642670929ed368121e4ebbe2',
        keys = {"8RZZW~r/BK+tGI'Il=)`}pj@g!z+j}4usU.g@"w{@6cLZMX^@3."L\%(zoP_[]j+", "LKZu4lB5}cN4YKz86,;+xy.Nn>Yk]]9KA+~GauG\e^HX=jz:^HD^|2%e)#&&;Ud3", "7s_E,8}yK(7-~FpQBT``6^g\Rm2R@%pDp9A{hhfC6,#zqL._D/IFa%@=H/Lc]a=4", "`!XZ40spHctE=kc{8k#25X_BeRXje@Km1`F&:^I2e&F#tZb\^(x"|Rm.2}>l4dK6", "-M,QFUO?g@4[a#nF2>VF|4a.OG#=,5Kd2LVI"*LVu(UZ=EP30[SLF"km=J\u[(7S"},
        iterations = 1168,
        checks = 0,
        memory_regions = {},
        
        -- Advanced environment checking
        verifyEnvironment = function(self)
            -- Check for debugging
            if debug.getinfo or debug.getupvalue or debug.setupvalue or debug.sethook then
                return false
            end
            
            -- Check for modified environment
            if _VERSION ~= "Lua 5.1" and _VERSION ~= "Lua 5.2" and _VERSION ~= "Lua 5.3" then
                return false
            end
            
            -- Check for suspicious global modifications
            for k,v in pairs(_G) do
                if type(v) == "function" and debug.getinfo(v).source ~= "=[C]" then
                    return false
                end
            end
            
            -- Memory integrity check
            for region, hash in pairs(self.memory_regions) do
                if self:calculateHash(region) ~= hash then
                    return false
                end
            end
            
            return true
        end,
        
        -- Advanced decryption system
        decrypt = function(self, encrypted_text)
            local result = encrypted_text
            for i = #self.keys, 1, -1 do
                local key = self.keys[i]
                -- Reverse substitution
                local unsubstituted = ''
                for c in result:gmatch('.') do
                    unsubstituted = unsubstituted .. string.char((ord(c) - #key) % 0x110000)
                end
                
                -- Base85 decode
                local decoded = base64.b85decode(unsubstituted)
                
                -- XOR decrypt
                result = ''
                for j = 1, #decoded do
                    result = result .. string.char(bit32.bxor(decoded:byte(j), key:byte((j-1) % #key + 1)))
                end
            end
            return result
        end,
        
        -- Memory protection system
        protectMemory = function(self, region, data)
            local hash = self:calculateHash(data)
            self.memory_regions[region] = hash
            return data
        end,
        
        -- Advanced hashing
        calculateHash = function(self, data)
            local hash = 0
            for i = 1, #data do
                hash = (hash * 33 + data:byte(i)) % 0xFFFFFFFF
            end
            return hash
        end,
        
        -- Anti-tamper system
        validateCodeIntegrity = function(self, code)
            local expected_hash = 'bc3114f27d5cb1fb38ae3b55d613e5acfd4498c436b32fc57305d65ce631490f'
            local actual_hash = self:calculateHash(code)
            return expected_hash == actual_hash
        end,
        
        -- Control flow protection
        obfuscateControlFlow = function(self, code)
            local parts = {}
            for line in code:gmatch("[^\n]+") do
                table.insert(parts, line)
            end
            
            local obfuscated = {}
            while #parts > 0 do
                local idx = math.random(1, #parts)
                table.insert(obfuscated, parts[idx])
                table.remove(parts, idx)
            end
            
            return table.concat(obfuscated, "\n")
        end
    }
    
    return security
end


local function executeSecureCode()
    local security = initAdvancedSecurity()
    local vm = createVM()
    
    -- Initialize protection systems
    local protected_env = setmetatable({
        -- Safe functions only
        print = print,
        type = type,
        tonumber = tonumber,
        tostring = tostring,
        select = select,
        unpack = unpack or table.unpack,
        -- Math functions
        math = {
            abs = math.abs,
            ceil = math.ceil,
            floor = math.floor,
            max = math.max,
            min = math.min,
            random = math.random,
            randomseed = math.randomseed,
        },
        -- String functions
        string = {
            byte = string.byte,
            char = string.char,
            format = string.format,
            len = string.len,
            lower = string.lower,
            upper = string.upper,
            sub = string.sub,
        },
        -- Table functions
        table = {
            insert = table.insert,
            remove = table.remove,
            sort = table.sort,
        },
    }, {
        __index = function(t, k)
            if security:verifyEnvironment() then
                return _G[k]
            end
            error('Security violation: Unauthorized access')
        end,
        __newindex = function()
            error('Security violation: Environment modification')
        end
    })

    -- Anti-debug hooks
    debug.sethook(function()
        if not security:verifyEnvironment() then
            error('Security violation: Debug detected')
        end
    end, "l", 1)

    local encrypted_code = [==[a­¶ ±µ°º~c¡f³}½£{pa­µa´vfa¬»§a|¨¶£a°xau³°rtya©¼aq­ew»©f¶±wra~£sq±°³¨²j²q´q²r§¸¬a~²¯ºye§r©w¶«´u}¤d¸£¯{º£³ya®®¨ia­¸³aª©k{r~´m s¯§xi¹d²afetªis¯§µ}­fqs±j£¼y·|du¹··xia­¶ª¯ya{ma«pa¡ a}jy±{«µrt®x·aµamfa¯a¬¥i~pea¯º¸¹µj§±»¨«¹¶a}º¦¦±»a}t´¸¸|¼³pam°d}ª~tµ¥a}½­aªµam¤qa{µ©¦´µ³ k{¹¦­a­s¸°¹¨¢¾´w»ªja¬£u¹¾sqa~´u¨r©¯}}q³¬´v«±½w®µc«¥k¶v§´mxwa~£a­µu}³k¹¨u¯§¨¹ §rw³¸wa~¦a¡a{·¸´a­w©³»iam¾a©½¾¬»xa¥a¬}uwmaa®h´½a«´qa{³a{»pf§ja© ¹¼|xfa¥»{v¦c~sa}|a|­jap·²i~¾µa©¾¢a~ka««·­e~½u­·¯¦µi~¹µkµ§¾¦~a{mwayd®a¬»²»¡ªp¦¯¬i»¼ª¹e®ki¼¬vx§«s¨²µya|pu¹r®va}¬rxy­qº¨a¹°aªºvxw²q­e¹c­yaaª{p©aªy¨´fcµ¦­k¤­e¸¸}¡¯a~wuamhep¬sf·±¯uµ«´¹»¹qa{ ¼ya«¯©¼sp½ª¶s¤t~tct­a|¸§±a~¨¸da{m¸{¡«±i«ja¬¬a{·r³¯ar®«a¨a©¯©¯fd¬¦d¦q¯µµak³ ­º²·¢»¸u«a|³va­¨e~¶~¬jhq·d~¶¬¢£rce¹¨fa~qx¬pea®ºr·µa|i­¤a¯ucvak´~uu´ua¯u´¸­¯¨m¯²¸¸d¯·®d¶£³¬´¹c­u}}¨§©¸dra¨¹®·a|¯¡¬a­¨f´ ºth p½ aamfa~ºm®j¬a©­»a©fm«²¡¦¸u³²¦ ®¶¤¬º¶sª¦¾§ª·º¢a}¬ua|ya{c³a·a~¨¸­awiaªx¨qa}f±´³¸¨°ca~²a¡¶x§x·k¨swa|r¶r}r¾·ayºyk¶v¨´e¹a|°¨»¥²§|¹§¾¢­fqhp§«aµjp³¹¨ºwe¯²¼¹¸¸~{a{u¯a¨³vºm²¢´f¦ayd{a}½t ¦t¡q³´p£°{r¢½­eºp¶´q££f°¥©¹º£hqm´f±§µ«§a}¨ja©~aªhea£§³ |°rf¨º~¹tcr£kt£«{xdi­£°{©·¶d|µ³|ap¸qa}¥©²sa« ±·²c¦«a~s©«±»ja}¬uuuµ}¤¦f¨²¬i»|¬µ¼mp|¼¯¾¯¤»¨£§§qu¡q²¯j¼º°¾°´{rvaª¤w·µ¦·²¹¨²§£ euam°µca¬ea©~a¬»a®}a{²f½¥±£am³¶£ª¤°§¾rpk§²«{p³x¬xv§¾x°a¬»r´av±²{¬§¾®¶¦x°rj¢¬jvª··~¯¸v¾u¹a~¡¯¨¶³}½£­ºt¶£ª³µ©´¯u»½·ae¹¤½«a~r ua¬¬rh¸|a®t}¶w¶v¦~a|©a«uq±dwam «´v³®a|½ama©~a|³a{m¼uw¤am¶a{yµ·£¨mcmyi¯m«{q³£¹¨µh¸«a­²a­±}«¦­fqhp§r·asµ®³¯·ªf¯a¬ uv¶·±h»ea~½¬a«§ª }¥q»£°»º²haªx«a¨du©±©jwµi~a}q¶¥a­a£¾ep¯²¬§x«¬¸u£j©¥{¯¸mwwx¸am¤a}½a¬¯hq®a¾r¹m¹´ia«d«a«p°a}{£~¨²©svr±¢aac¢¶©¯f´´»wa¬qf·ama®¥a~½³a}¬ra©ºµ¸a~©aª¶´¢ªvu®©¤»¹¯¸kf³©©¡aja®{keª¬ka¬qe½qªh¨§½¬¡½°¹amfha{©º©a©~«¥ª¬my²¯¹q²¦½©¤««¤¯·p­ha«u¨w³|¸~~ ¯a¯ykdua{¶e®¶u¨²jx­°°d{ua©risa{³ a­¬a´yªa®fak¼«¯u¹®xvwº²h¸a||ak}µ½a®·®ja®º²a¬}y~¢i|¯u¸­«´¾ta¥aª©ha­µa~£x­®¬¨¨ºº²hª½y£¬²¯iuw·»´u­£¸²¤ft|u¥§©v¶µrª®d´©±q°r°©¬º¾®x¨¤a¥¸¨²¸·²e¨x¥|a­±}dak±ma«u¦am¶½a}½tk­´ia{aªcma¯|a¹©w©¯}qa³}¾y·´´sªja~q­¬|i½a~½¶ph¤¨¡mx¸paª»ya~p¨¬ºª»º{¸ a®h´|da|xa¨¹±³°p£°µ°«a{a|a{aj~a­­fa}¬rxa¬¬¹a«¹§a©­akia´v³a|¼cw¬a~²¥a­w¦¬»­±§µ| ª½yra{µu±¢­®a½hu¼¢§ri¨±´x´a}½a~©xdi¼¶¸«¶ª´mm¨¨®´j¼©£aªx§ma¯ªu¯«±¦»¤²a¬}am¦~§µ»¦·«©¸¢¾qµªxqª¼ha}¬ur¡«d¦¤f²t²¯iuw¨±º´¯²§µ¼²u´{s¾³uq··°paa~¨¸a¨jµa­«»®­y~a~¤m°¬¾¸uaª©¬{am¯c©w½r®x¤¯¸ h¹q°ua}µ¦µca~¦¬a±°am½² ³£¤³µc«a­´¨ a©­ c¢ªy­¦tc­¹t­²µ¼ª¨x{j¨²|¨³²¶´u°¾·µhca}µx­aª}½°©£ap³¾cm¨» dµ¦·ce°®°r¸¬»jam­ta|¦¯amx¯¸ i«¹´jam|kq{¥m²r´¯©¢½h·¸¡­a~k}³y¹t¬i¼|¯a|¯s¶xma~®a¬£x¬a¡©¼a®hµpq¼¸ha~pt³­a·pe¶£²²»q¡©eaª©fka}µ¶q§¸¸amy­x¤¢ª©¨©¥¥¾«©f~´¶«©·¾¹µk·°a©­p~®mµp±pm{q~¨¦®£x¦}»§µ½a|ya{­ja{x¡{~°µ¨¹e©¹a{h«°¾yp}a|uu{a«¸­³¡vs«vhu¨¹£aªi¢«aª»v®aªµs¡qªa£­®¡i¹µº¦º´u®wah¡aªtka}ea®h´¦r½²¼fsf¶µi¾©aydfj²¯j¥¬¹©vº§rf½y~e|¦i¹a¯­a|i­£a~~ ¯ª¬ºd¨¯a©pa¨¬»·a»¶«{y¯aµa¬£uf¢wuuª ²r½a»¡¬juq»a°¾´º¨°±«¢³¶e»ª°º²hvx±¯tª¡|ra¨j·~aª¦·e}¯¸m£¢­¾´²a{q¾³}½¢£¦«©¯§mu¯x¯a|¾°rªav~~§ram|iam½x´t®u¥®k­fq¡­³¢µi¾¨«©f|}²­fs©¯¯¨~¾fa« a®¹a¬r¥®¡¹¹´{sqµi¾¥¨»a¬¬©a{¶¥h°µhµ¢­ }a®·®|a¦a±am¾a®a¡¼am­ta«¢f¥¨e³®¬jvd¡a®®¨ªam a    
    -- Execution environment setup
    setfenv(1, protected_env)
    
    -- Memory protection
    security:protectMemory('code', encrypted_code)
    
    -- Integrity verification
    if not security:validateCodeIntegrity(encrypted_code) then
        error('Security violation: Code tampering detected')
    end
    
    -- Decrypt and execute
    local decrypted = security:decrypt(encrypted_code)
    local chunk = load(decrypted, 'protected_chunk', 't', protected_env)
    
    if chunk then
        return chunk()
    end
end

return (function()
    local success, result = pcall(executeSecureCode)
    if not success then
        error('Runtime security: ' .. tostring(result))
    end
    return result
end)()
